export const programmingLanguages = [
    "JavaScript",
    "Python",
    "Java",
    "C++",
    "C#",
    "TypeScript",
    "Go",
    "Swift",
    "Kotlin",
    "PHP",
    "Ruby",
    "Rust",
  ];
  
  // Mapping languages to unique colors
  export const languageColors = {
    JavaScript: "#F7DF1E",
    Python: "#3776AB",
    Java: "#ED8B00",
    "C++": "#00599C",
    "C#": "#9B4F96",
    TypeScript: "#3178C6",
    Go: "#00ADD8",
    Swift: "#FA7343",
    Kotlin: "#A97BFF",
    PHP: "#777BB4",
    Ruby: "#CC342D",
    Rust: "#DEA584",
  };
  
  // Mapping each programming language to its versions
  export const languageVersions = {
    JavaScript: ["ES5", "ES6", "ES7", "ES8", "ES9", "ES10"],
    Python: ["2.7", "3.6", "3.7", "3.8", "3.9", "3.10", "3.11"],
    Java: ["8", "11", "15", "17", "21"],
    "C++": ["98", "03", "11", "14", "17", "20", "23"],
    "C#": ["5.0", "6.0", "7.0", "8.0", "9.0", "10.0", "11.0"],
    TypeScript: ["2.x", "3.x", "4.x", "5.x"],
    Go: ["1.14", "1.15", "1.16", "1.17", "1.18", "1.19"],
    Swift: ["4.2", "5.0", "5.1", "5.2", "5.3", "5.4", "5.5", "5.6"],
    Kotlin: ["1.3", "1.4", "1.5", "1.6", "1.7", "1.8"],
    PHP: ["5.6", "7.0", "7.1", "7.2", "7.3", "7.4", "8.0", "8.1"],
    Ruby: ["2.5", "2.6", "2.7", "3.0", "3.1", "3.2"],
    Rust: ["2015", "2018", "2021"],
  };
  
  // Tags data for each language
 export const tagsData = {
    JavaScript: ["React", "Node.js", "ES6", "TypeScript", "Frontend", "Backend"],
    Python: ["Django", "Flask", "Machine Learning", "Data Science", "Automation"],
    Java: ["Spring Boot", "Hibernate", "Android", "Microservices", "JVM"],
    CSharp: [".NET", "ASP.NET", "Blazor", "Unity", "Xamarin"],
    PHP: ["Laravel", "Symfony", "WordPress", "Backend", "API Development"],
    Swift: ["iOS", "SwiftUI", "Xcode", "Mobile Development"],
    Go: ["Golang", "Concurrency", "Microservices", "Cloud"],
  };
